headline: Staples and Discretionary Stocks Are Soaring Together. That's Not Supposed to Happen.
summary: Staples and discretionary are often viewed by traders as opposites, so they don't often rally together.  The S&P's discretionary sector was up 2.3%, while staples were up 1.9%.  It happened two times in 2024 and three times in 2023, according to Dow Jones Market Data.

headline: Sonrava Health Welcomes Tony Caskey as President of Clinic Operations for DentalWorks
summary: ORANGE, Calif., August 06, 2025--Sonrava Health, a national family of dental brands including Western Dental, Brident, DentalWorks, and Perfect Teeth, is pleased to announce the appointment of Tony Caskey as President, Clinic Operations – DentalWorks.

headline: Tree Hut Unmasks 'Eerie-Sistible' Fall Line to Kick Off the Spookiest Season Yet
summary: With Summer-ween in full swing, Tree Hut, America's No. 1 Body Scrub brand, is embracing the moment with the launch of its limited-edition Glow Potion Collection. This Halloween-inspired release blends nostalgic packaging with indulgent skincare, pairing fan-favorite product formats with festive new scents. The collection includes four spooky scents that are sure to bewitch consumers' body care routine – Sweet Punkin, Meyow, Frankenshine, and Scare Glow.
